vernments%20and%20regulated%20firms%20want%20AI%20that%20they%20can%20control%20without%20US%20providers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20power%20will%20be%20multipolar%2C%20favoring%20regional%20players%20over%20Silicon%20Valley%20giants%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20race%20to%20dominate%20AI%20accelerates%2C%20Europe's%20most%20prominent%20AI%20startup%20is%20betting%20that%20geography%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20technology%20%E2%80%94%20can%20be%20a%20competitive%20advantage%20in%20its%20home%20market.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArthur%20Mensch%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistral-ai-ceo-risk-ai-lazy-deskilling-dario-amodei-jobs-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFrench%20AI%20company%20Mistral%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20the%20company's%20edge%20in%20Europe%20over%20Silicon%20Valley%20rivals%20like%20OpenAI%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Anthropic%20isn't%20about%20having%20dramatically%20smarter%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20said%20that%20many%20European%20governments%20and%20regulated%20enterprises%20are%20seeking%20AI%20systems%20they%20can%20control%2C%20customize%2C%20and%20operate%20independently%2C%20rather%20than%20relying%20on%20a%20small%20number%20of%20external%20providers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEuropean%20governments%20are%20coming%20to%20us%20because%20they%20want%20to%20build%20the%20technology%20and%20they%20want%20to%20serve%20their%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20Mensch%20said%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BBig%20Technology%20Podcast%26quot%3B%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2289000083-6f3d-4080-b5b2-7567a1a1f66c%5C%22%3EWhen%20models%20converge%2C%20control%20becomes%20the%20moat%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMistral%2C%20founded%20in%202023%20and%20now%20valued%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistral-funding-asml-chips-ai-europe-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eroughly%20%2414%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20develops%20large%20language%20models%20that%20rival%20those%20of%20leading%20US%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Mensch%20said%20that%20frontier%20AI%20models%20are%20rapidly%20converging%20in%20performance%20as%20research%20spreads%20and%20training%20techniques%20become%20widely%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20the%20real%20battleground%20is%20shifting%20away%20from%20raw%20intelligence%20and%20toward%20deployment%2C%20control%2C%20and%20trust%20%E2%80%94%20a%20shift%20that%20plays%20directly%20into%20Mistral's%20pitch%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMensch%20said%20governments%2C%20banks%2C%20and%20heavily%20regulated%20industries%20want%20AI%20systems%20they%20can%20customize%2C%20deploy%20locally%2C%20and%20operate%20independently%20%E2%80%94%20without%20fear%20that%20a%20single%20vendor%20could%20change%20the%20rules%20or%20shut%20off%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20approach%20has%20already%20paid%20off.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startup-mistral-lands-french-military-deal-openai-of-europe-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrance's%20military%20recently%20selected%20Mistral%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20an%20AI%20deal%20that%20keeps%20sensitive%20systems%20running%20on%20French-controlled%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2216e14480-75b7-454a-aac5-9c5f6f4f114c%5C%22%3EAI%20sovereignty%20beats%20regulatory%20arbitrage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMensch%20pushed%20back%20on%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20company%20benefits%20merely%20from%20EU%20regulation%20or%20protectionism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20framed%20the%20demand%20as%20geopolitical%20and%20operational.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEuropean%20governments%2C%20he%20said%2C%20want%20AI%20that%20they%20can%20govern%20themselves%20and%20use%20to%20serve%20citizens%20without%20depending%20on%20foreign%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20logic%20applies%20to%20regulated%20enterprises%20that%20need%20tighter%20control%20over%20data%2C%20compliance%2C%20and%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMistral's%20embrace%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistral-ceo-deepseek-open-source-ai-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eopen-source%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20central%20to%20that%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpen%20source%20allows%20customers%20to%20run%20AI%20on%20their%20own%20infrastructure%2C%20build%20redundancy%2C%20and%20avoid%20vendor%20lock-in%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20the%20closed%2C%20centralized%20platforms%20favored%20by%20many%20US%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b09f979f-ddd5-4958-836e-006ff5765acf%5C%22%3EA%20multi-polar%20AI%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20appeal%20isn't%20limited%20to%20Europe.%20Mensch%20said%20Mistral%20also%20works%20with%20US%20and%20Asian%20customers%20who%20want%20to%20reduce%20dependence%20on%20a%20small%20group%20of%20American%20providers%20and%20retain%20more%20autonomy%20over%20how%20AI%20is%20used%20inside%20their%20organizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20approach%20is%20already%20extending%20beyond%20the%20West.%20Mistral%20recently%20deepened%20a%20partnership%20with%20Morocco's%20government%20to%20co-build%20locally%20tailored%20AI%20models%20and%20launch%20a%20joint%20research%20and%20development%20lab%20aimed%20at%20strengthening%20the%20country's%20technological%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELong%20term%2C%20Mensch%20said%20he%20doesn't%20believe%20AI%20will%20be%20dominated%20by%20a%20single%20winner%20or%20country.%20Instead%2C%20he%20expects%20multiple%20regional%20centers%20of%20expertise%20shaped%20by%20local%20needs%2C%20industries%2C%20and%20political%20realities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20future%2C%20he%20suggested%2C%20Mistral's%20biggest%20advantage%20may%20not%20be%20the%20models%20it%20builds%20%E2%80%94%20but%20where%2C%20and%20how%2C%20it%20builds%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20Mistral%20and%20have%20a%20tip%20or%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3