egatively%20on%20recruiters%2C%20but%20in%20the%20current%20landscape%2C%20there's%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20AI%20washing%20going%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20makes%20it%20hard%20to%20differentiate%20the%20real%20wins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompanies%20are%20talking%20about%20all%20these%20things%20they're%20doing%20and%20how%20they're%20slapping%20AI%20on%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20they're%20actually%20not%20doing%20interesting%20things%20with%20work%20or%20with%20products.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20mobilizing%20executives%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fciscos-cpo-shares-2-most-valuable-skills-engineers-ai-era-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECisco's%20president%20and%20chief%20product%20officer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Jeetu%20Patel%2C%20has%20helped%20score%20some%20of%20those%20top%20candidates.%20She%20said%20when%20the%20company%20has%20a%20strong%20AI%20candidate%2C%20he'll%20pick%20up%20the%20phone%20and%20give%20them%20a%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there's%20someone%20that%20we%20are%20really%20strategically%20trying%20to%20hire%2C%20we%20will%20get%20him%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatel%2C%20whom%20the%20company%20poached%20from%20Box%20in%202020%2C%20understands%20the%20connection%20between%20having%20the%20best%20people%20design%20products%20and%20the%20success%20of%20those%20products%2C%20Jones%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECisco%20isn't%20the%20only%20company%20to%20use%20this%20technique.%20Citadel%20CTO%20Umesh%20Subramanian%20recently%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitadel-cto-personally-calls-candidates-to-recruit-talent-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epersonally%20calls%20top%20entry-level%20candidates%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20hiring%20process%20to%20talk%20through%20their%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20Sam%20Altman%20has%20also%20reportedly%20called%20candidates%20to%20convince%20them%20to%20join%20the%20AI%20company%2C%20and%20Meta%20CEO%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20previously%20appeared%20in%20email%20chains%20to%20recruit%20talent%20and%20has%20also%20reportedly%20hosted%20top%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-talent-wars-recruiting-hiring-white-hot-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecandidates%20at%20his%20home%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fce42619-c5a5-440e-9f8d-bc07cc37f896%5C%22%3EFinding%20the%20right%20talent%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20qualifies%20a%20candidate%20to%20get%20a%20phone%20call%20from%20Cisco's%20Patel%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20%26quot%3Btop-tier%26quot%3B%20technical%20skills%20and%20experience%2C%20Jones%20assesses%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoft-skills-you-need-in-ai-era-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebehavior%20and%20potential%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20evaluating%20top%20talent.%20She%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20about%20skills%2C%26quot%3B%20because%20those%20can%20be%20learned%2C%20but%20also%20about%20the%20leadership%20characteristics%20an%20applicant%20has.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20know%2C%20not%20only%20have%20you%20done%20these%20things%2C%20but%20are%20you%20intellectually%20curious%3F%20Are%20you%20intellectually%20and%20emotionally%20agile%3F%20Are%20you%20someone%20who%20brings%20your%20team%20along%20with%20you%3F%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20said%20that%20the%20company%20also%20has%20to%20put%20its%20efforts%20toward%20%26quot%3Bnaturally%26quot%3B%20attracting%20talent%20both%20online%20and%20in%20person%20by%20creating%20a%20presence%20in%20the%20tech%20community.%20She%20said%20that%20include