%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20feeling%20that%20we're%20falling%20behind%20at%2037%20Signals%20in%20terms%20of%20our%20ability%20to%20produce%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20our%20ability%20to%20launch%20things%20or%20improve%20the%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20this%20is%20why%20I'm%20a%20little%20skeptical%20about%20the%20claims%20that%20AI%20is%20already%20now%20at%20a%20place%20where%20you%20can%20take%20your%20standard%20SaaS%20business%20and%20then%20fire%20half%20the%20programmers%20and%20still%20go%20faster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FuWqno4HM4xA%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22DHH%3A%20Why%20AI%20Isn't%20Writing%20My%20Code%20(Yet)%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EHumans%20coded%2095%25%20of%20the%20code%20for%20Fizzy%2C%2037%20Signals'%20Kanban-inspired%20organization%20product%2C%20Hansson%20said.%20They've%20experienced%20with%20AI-powered%20features%20for%20the%20product%2C%20but%20for%20now%2C%20they've%20ended%20up%20on%20the%20cutting%20room%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHansson%20said%20he%20doesn't%20see%20his%20business%20losing%20ground%20because%20he's%20focusing%20on%20writing%20his%20own%20code.%20For%20the%20time%20being%2C%20he%20can%20still%20%26quot%3Bcare%20about%20the%20beauty%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20luxury%20that%20perhaps%20is%20akin%20to%20what%20a%20modern%20saddle%20maker%20enjoys%20when%20you%20go%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20the%20letter's%20just%20right%2C%20and%20the%20stitching%20is%20just%20right.'%20And%20you're%20like%2C%20'Okay%2C%20but%20you're%20no%20longer%20part%20of%20the%20main%20production%20for%20transportation%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I'm%20like%2C%20'Well%2C%20so%20what%3F'%20I'll%20continue%20to%20make%20my%20handwritten%20code%20saddles%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can%20for%20my%20enjoyment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2224e404b7-729d-40af-901a-4cda0638d624%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Just%20try%20to%20hold%20onto%20your%20hat'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlternatively%2C%20Hansson%20said%20he's%20seen%20the%20promise%20of%20AI%20in%20the%20type%20of%20tools%20Shopify%20uses%2C%20where%20he%20serves%20on%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20things%20that%20they've%20done%20with%20SiteKick%2C%20the%20AI%20agent%20they%20have%20helping%20merchants%20set%20up%20their%20shop%20and%20optimize%20their%20shop%20is%20truly%20incredible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20there's%20some%20real%20tangible%20benefits%20in%20that%20that%20I%20think%20are%20undisputable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Hansson%20said%20he's%20excited%20about%20the%20promise%20of%20a%20new%20era%20that%20could%20upend%20development%2C%20just%20as%20the%20iPhone's%202007%20release%20ushered%20in%20a%20focus%20on%20mobile%20optimization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20one%20where%20we%2C%20in%20real%20time%2C%20know%20the%20world%20is%20going%20to%20look%20totally%20different%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20know%20what%20the%20final%20result%20is%20going%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20think%20the%20best%20thing%20you%20can%20just%20do%20is%20accept%20that%20A%2C%20we%20don't%20know%2C%20B%2C%20that%20it's%20really%20exciting%2C%20and%20C%2C%20just%20try%20to%20hold%20onto%20your%20hat%2C%20jump%20on%20there%20cowboy%20and%20ride%20it%20and%20see%20where%20it%20goes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20AI%20isn't%20going%20away%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20some%20people%20may%20hope.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20power%20does%20not%20exist.%20You%20don't%20get%20to%20roll%20these%20things%