%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20and%20made%20a%20profit%20of%20%242%20million%20on%20%2440%20million%20in%20revenue.%20If%20you're%20making%20money%2C%20why%20did%20you%20raise%20more%20money%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustin%20Smith%3A%20If%20you've%20been%20in%20the%20media%20business%20for%2030%20years%2C%20you%20know%20the%20media%20business%20is%20pretty%20unpredictable.%20Just%20because%20you've%20had%20a%20good%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20and%20you've%20developed%20what%20we%20think%20is%20a%20really%20interesting%20model%20%E2%80%94%20if%20there's%20a%20chance%20to%20raise%20money%2C%20with%20good%20long-term%20investors%2C%20to%20accelerate%20the%20things%20that%20are%20working%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20feel%20like%20it's%20taken%20three%20years%2C%20but%20we've%20got%20the%20foundation%20of%20what%20we%20believe%20is%20an%20interesting%20innovation%20in%20the%20media%20space.%20It's%20a%20new%20formula%20that%20is%20working%2C%20and%20we%20feel%20like%20we%20can%20extend%20it%20across%20the%20world%20and%20across%20new%20markets%2C%20and%20that's%20what%20we're%20going%20to%20use%20the%20new%20capital%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESemafor%20has%20leaned%20heavily%20into%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.semafor.com%2Fevents%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Eevents%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20since%20you%20launched%2C%20and%20you%20say%2050%25%20of%20your%20revenue%20comes%20from%20events.%20But%20that's%20a%20very%20hard%20business%20to%20scale.%20How%20do%20you%20think%20you'll%20grow%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20did%20almost%20a%20hundred%20events%20this%20year.%20But%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20energy%20and%20focus%20of%20our%20event%20strategy%20is%20around%20some%20of%20the%20bigger%20convenings%20that%20we%20do.%20As%20we%20go%20forward%2C%20the%20idea%20is%20not%20necessarily%20to%20go%20from%20a%20hundred%20to%20200%20to%20300%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strategy%20is%20much%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20to%20build%20a%20series%20of%20tentpoles%20that%20themselves%20become%20larger%2C%20more%20significant%2C%20more%20valuable%20commercially%2C%20more%20influential%20editorially.%20That's%20how%20you%20scale%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20seen%20people%20talking%20about%20your%20ambition%20to%20take%20on%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flive.businessinsider.com%2Fevents%2Fworld-economic-forum%3Futm_source%3Dpressroom%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDavos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20the%20annual%20global%20business%2Fpolicy%20conference%20happening%20this%20month.%20Is%20that%20a%20real%20plan%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20started%20Semafor%2C%20in%20the%20original%20business%20plan%20deck%2C%20we%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20build%20a%20leading%20CEO%20convening%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20We%20looked%20at%20the%20US%20market%2C%20and%20we%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20interesting.%20This%20is%20the%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20there%20is%20not%20a%20dominant%20leading%20CEO%20convening%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20thought%20that%20was%20an%20interesting%20fact%2C%20which%20presented%20an%20opportunity.%20So%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20we%20envisioned%20building%20this%20from%20scratch.%20And%20we%20identified%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20as%20the%20best%20location%20to%20do%20this%2C%20which%20was%20also%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20an%20unusual%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDC's%20historically%20not%20been%20a%20place%20where%20CEOs%20travel.%20It's%20not%20been%20historically%20a%20center%20of%20business%2C%20but%20that%20of%20course%20has%20been%20changing%20across%20the%20last%20five%20to%20seven%20years%3A%20The%20role%20of%20geopolitics%20in%20the%20boardroom%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20regulation%20%E2%80%94%20all%20these%20different%20trends%20have%20converged%20and%20now%20CEOs%20from%20both%20the%20United%20States%20and%20across%20the%20world%20find%20themselves%20in%20Washington%20three%2C%20four%2C%20five%2C%2010%20times%20a%20year.%20And%20we%20were%20fortunate%20because%20we%20made%20that%20bet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeter%3A%20You've%20been%20describing%20a%20business%20that's%20very%20DC-based.%20You%20are%20based%20in%20DC.%20It's%20really%20striking%20that%20some%20of%20the%20most%20successful%20media%20startups%20of%20the%20last%20few%20years%20%E2%80%94%20you%20guys%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAxios%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpunchbowl.news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPunchbowl%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpuck.news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPuck%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20to%20some%20extent%20%E2%80%94%20are%20all%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Frecode%2F23297459%2Faxios-facebook-advertising-tech-google-peter-kafka-column%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Emaking%20money%20or%20trying%20to%20make%20money%20in%20Washington%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20by%20matching%20advertisers%20with%20powerful%20people.%20How%20much%20bigger%20can%20that%20market%20get%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20effectively%20a%20B2B%20marketplace.%20What's%20sometimes%20confusing%20to%20people%20is%20that%20many%20of%20these%20news%20properties%2C%20including%20Semafor%2C%20are%20consumer-facing%20now%20%E2%80%94%20consumer%20web%20pages%20and%20consumer-focused%20newsletters.%20But%20since%20the%20audience%20that%20they're%20appealing%20to%20is%20this%20segment%20of%20this%20leadership%20audience%2C%20it%20allows%20for%20a%20much%20more%20targeted%20type%20of%20business%20monetization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20it's%20the%20corporate%20affairs%20market%2C%20which%20is%20largely%20corporate%20reputation.%20There's%20also%20a%20bit%20of%20advocacy%20advertising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cato.org%2Fcommentary%2Fabout-those-facebook-ads-calling-more-internet-regulation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFacebook%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20healthy%20regulation%20is%20a%20great%20idea.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExactly.%20This%20market%20has%20existed%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20and%20there%20was%20a%20whole%20predecessor%20group%20of%20brands%20before%20Politico%20and%20Axios.%20You%20may%20remember%20Roll%20Call%2C%20or%20the%20Hill%2C%20or%20National%20Journal.%20Those%20were%20some%20of%20the%20most%20successful%20and%20profitable%20and%20commercially%20viable%20media%20businesses%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20these%20new%20digital%20disruptors%20came%20along%20and%20stole%20the%20market%20from%20those%20legacy%20players.%20But%20I%20think%20what%20also%20happened%20is%20that%20the%20market%20grew%20really%2C%20really%20dramatically%20because%20the%20intersection%20of%20government%20and%20business%20has%20become%20more%20pronounced%20and%20more%20intense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintel-donald-trump-buy-stake-us-other-companies-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20stakes%20have%20gotten%20higher%20and%20higher%20and%20higher%20for%20companies%20operating%20in%20the%20US%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20their%20needs%20to%20communicate%20their%20corporate%20brand%20positions%20have%20gotten%20more%20urgent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20had%20heard%20early%20on%20that%20you%20guys%20were%20going%20to%20make%20your%20version%20of%20the%20networks'%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FSunday_morning_talk_show%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESun