r-of-ai-geoffrey-hinton-2026-job-losses-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGeoffrey%20Hinton%3C%2Fa%3E%20predicted%20that%20AI%20would%20eradicate%20many%20radiology%20jobs%20and%20advised%20students%20to%20avoid%20the%20field.%20The%20opposite%20happened.%20While%20AI%20is%20automating%20many%20radiology%20%3Cem%3Etasks%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20there%20are%20actually%20more%20radiologists%20employed%20now%20than%20when%20Hinton%20made%20his%20prediction%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20killer%20stats%2C%20shared%20in%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worksinprogress.news%2Fp%2Fwhy-ai-isnt-replacing-radiologists%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2025%20blog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20describes%20why%20radiologists%20are%20still%20in%20huge%20demand%3A%20In%202025%2C%20American%20diagnostic%20radiology%20residency%20programs%20offered%20a%20record%201%2C208%20positions%2C%20a%204%25%20increase%20from%202024%2C%20and%20the%20field's%20vacancy%20rates%20are%20at%20all-time%20highs.%20Also%2C%20in%202025%2C%20radiology%20was%20the%20second-highest-paid%20medical%20specialty%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20an%20average%20income%20of%20%24520%2C000%2C%20over%2048%25%20percent%20higher%20than%20the%20average%20radiologist%20salary%20in%202015%20(the%20year%20before%20Hinton's%20prediction).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20did%20this%20happen%3F%20Huang%20argued%20that%20the%20job's%20purpose%20isn't%20%26quot%3Breading%20scans.%26quot%3B%20Those%20are%20tasks%20that%20AI%20has%20automated.%20The%20true%20purpose%20of%20a%20radiologist%20is%20to%20diagnose%20disease%2C%20guide%20treatment%2C%20and%20support%20those%20efforts%20with%20research.%20When%20AI%20helps%20clinicians%20evaluate%20more%20images%20with%20higher%20confidence%2C%20hospitals%20can%20serve%20more%20patients%2C%20generate%20more%20revenue%2C%20and%20justify%20hiring%20more%20specialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298aa9562-5752-4738-956f-2a62e3207632%5C%22%3EIs%20typing%20really%20a%20job%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20logic%2C%20he%20said%2C%20applies%20across%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20spend%20most%20of%20my%20day%20typing%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20noted%2C%20describing%20typing%20as%20a%20task%2C%20not%20his%20job's%20purpose.%20Tools%20that%20automate%20writing%20don't%20eliminate%20the%20need%20for%20executives%3B%20they%20often%20expand%20the%20amount%20of%20work%20leaders%20and%20other%20employees%20can%20take%20on%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20somebody%20could%20use%20AI%20to%20automate%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20typing%20%E2%80%94%20I%20really%20appreciate%20that%2C%20and%20it%20helps%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20hasn't%20really%20made%20me%2C%20if%20you%20will%2C%20less%20busy.%20In%20a%20lot%20of%20ways%2C%20I%20become%20more%20busy%20because%20I'm%20able%20to%20do%20more%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229055b824-4d9a-4a98-9cda-4474230c5ae2%5C%22%3ECoding%2C%20law%2C%20and%20restaurants%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20%26quot%3Btask%20versus%20purpose%26quot%3B%20framework%20is%20increasingly%20visible%20in%20knowledge%20work%2C%20where%20AI%20tools%20are%20speeding%20up%20and%20automating%20tasks%20such%20as%20drafting%2C%20summarizing%2C%20and%20generating%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20pointed%20to%20software%20engineering%20as%20a%20case%20where%20AI%20can%20reduce%20time%20spent%20on%20a%20core%20task%20(writing%20code)%20while%20raising%20demand%20for%20the%20job's%20purpose%3A%20solving%20problems%20and%20identifying%20new%20ones%20worth%20solving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20hiring%20aggressively%20even%20as%20AI%20coding%20tools%20such%20as%20Cursor%20spread%20through%20the%20company's%20engineering%20teams%2C%20because%20productivity%20gains%20allow%20companies%20to%20pursue%20more%20ideas.%20That%20can%20boost%20revenue%2C%20leaving%20more%20money%20to%20hire%20new%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaw%20is%20another%20example%20he%20cited.%20Reading%20and%20drafting%20contracts%20are%20tasks%2C%20while%20the%20purpose%20of%20a%20lawyer%20is%20to%20protect%20clients%20and%20resolve%20disputes.%20AI%20can%20accelerate%20document-heavy%20work%2C%20but%20the%20role's%20true%20value%20relies%20on%20judgment%2C%20strategy%2C%20and%20accountability%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you%20need%20experienced%2C%20trustworthy%20human%20attorneys%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20even%20applies%20to%20waiters%20working%20in%20a%20restaurant.%20Their%20task%20is%20taking%20food%20orders%2C%20but%20their%20purpose%20is%20to%20ensure%20guests%20have%20a%20great%20time%2C%20Huang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20some%20AI%20is%20taking%20the%20order%20or%20even%20delivering%20the%20food%2C%20their%20job%20is%20still%20helping%20us%20have%20a%20great%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20added.%20%26quot%3BThey%20would%20reshape%20their%20jobs%20accordingly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang's%20argument%20isn't%20that%20AI%20won't%20disrupt%20roles%20%E2%80%94%20it%20will.%20But%20he%20contends%20the%20early%20evidence%20points%20less%20toward%20a%20wholesale%20collapse%20of%20employment%20and%20more%20toward%20job%20redesign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20workers%2C%20the%20implication%20is%20pragmatic%3A%20if%20your%20role%20is%20defined%20primarily%20by%20a%20repeatable%20task%2C%20AI%20is%20a%20direct%20threat.%20If%20it's%20anchored%20in%20outcomes%20%E2%80%94%20diagnosis%2C%20customer%20experience%2C%20problem-solving%2C%20conflict%20resolution%20%E2%80%94%20AI%20may%20be%20less%20a%20replacement%20than%20a%20lever%2C%20changing%20what%20you%20spend%20time%20on%20while%20keeping%20your%20job's%20purpose%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20