uote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20small%20homes%20on%20the%20property%20for%20overnight%20stays%2C%20built%20without%20cement%20and%20bricks%2C%20using%20prefabricated%20construction%20methods.%20Jai%20emphasises%20that%20this%20is%20not%20an%20eco-tourism%20spot%20but%20rather%20a%20model%20intended%20to%20inspire%20others%20who%20wish%20to%20rewild%20their%20own%20spaces.%20He%20has%20also%20written%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20subject%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20motivate%20others%20to%20take%20similar%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20already%20feel%20like%20the%20richest%20person%20on%20the%20planet.%20I%20have%20created%20more%20wealth%20over%20the%20past%202.5%20years%20than%20in%20the%2050%20years%20before%20that.%20One%20must%20realise%20that%20richness%20is%20not%20in%20our%2030%2C000%20sq%20ft%20mansions%20and%20apartments%20in%20cities.%20The%20richness%20lies%20in%20mental%20peace%2C%20which%20I%E2%80%99ve%20found.%20Most%20days%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20even%20walking%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20levitating%20in%20the%20biosphere%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20too%20adds%20that%20he%20has%20received%20calls%20from%20people%20across%20the%20country%20interested%20in%20replicating%20this%20initiative.%20The%20message%20the%20duo%20want%20to%20give%20out%20is%20clear%20as%20day%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20go%20back%20to%20the%20simpler%20things%20and%20reconnect%20with%20nature.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EImages%20Courtesy%20Jai%20Dhar%20Gupta%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757331000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji2-1724829336.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D498044%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20the%20movie%20Avatar%2C%20environmentalist%20and%20clean%20air%20activist%20Jai%20Dhar%20Gupta%20turned%2032%20acres%20near%20Uttarakhand's%20Rajaji%20National%20Park%20into%20a%20biosp